          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Canadian Investment Regulatory Organization (CIRO)\nYou may also submit your complaint to CIRO, which is the self-regulatory organization in Canada to which CIBC World Markets Inc. and CIBC Investor Services Inc. are registered members. CIBC Wood Gundy is a division of CIBC World Markets Inc. CIBC Investor\u2019s Edge, CIBC Imperial Investor Services, and CIBC Private Banking are divisions of CIBC Investor Services Inc. CIRO has a dedicated Complaints and Inquiries department, which you can contact by phone, email or mail.",
